  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO DEFINE THE TERMS \"ADULT PERFORMANCE,\" \"PERFORMANCE HARMFUL TO MINORS,\" AND \"OBSCENITY\"; TO PROHIBIT THE PERFORMANCE IN OR EXHIBITION OF AN ADULT PERFORMANCE ON PUBLIC PROPERTY OR IN A LOCATION WHERE THE ADULT PERFORMANCE COULD BE VIEWED BY A MINOR; TO PROHIBIT A STATE AGENCY OR POLITICAL SUBDIVISION FROM EXHIBITING OR FUNDING, IN WHOLE OR IN PART WITH PUBLIC FUNDS, AN ADULT PERFORMANCE; TO CREATE A CIVIL CAUSE OF ACTION AS A REMEDY FOR VIOLATION OF THIS SECTION; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
